Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:41.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mushi-shi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:43.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko is my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:47.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hear that you have prophetic dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:55.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I think that your dreams could pose a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:49.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're well known around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:01:58.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:01.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that Mushi are involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:04.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Mushi in your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:07.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're the ones causing you to have prophetic dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you'll have them more frequently.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:12.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should adjust them with this medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:16.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How often do you have these dreams right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:20.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once or twice every ten days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:22.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eventually you'll have four or five.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:24.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that point, you should take these.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:28.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's poisonous if you take more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:34.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you leave it untreated, at some point\Nyou will not awaken from your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:37.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's important is moderation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:40.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be sure to take them, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:44.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be back by the time they run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:48.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until then,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:52.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,sweet dreams.
