Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.15,0:03:01.11,ep-title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2400,0)\be1}The Pillow Pathway
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:07.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Do not converse with one talking in their sleep."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:12.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is the wisdom of the world beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:25.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It hasn't even been a year since I last came.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:30.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What in the world happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mushi-shi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:05.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you. I want to ask you some things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:13.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This town... did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:15.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:21.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you what happened. Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:39.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:42.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:49.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:53.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a water channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:58.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We could expand the farm fields with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:09.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, we found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:12.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jin did it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:14.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell the townspeople.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:24.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The farmers gave us all this as a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel a little guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:29.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:34.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can hardly feed her anything good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:36.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should be thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:38.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yamamomo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:40.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Jin,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:45.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,you're having more prophetic dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:48.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just like that Mushi-shi said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:53.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really believe him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:56.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Mushi are giving me these dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:06:00.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know. But what if...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:03.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if he's right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:06.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:09.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take the medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:11.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:13.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:18.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The western cliff collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:28.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for your dream, we'd all be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:31.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to thank you enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:43.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kinu, sometimes I get worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:48.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,When what I see in my dream becomes real...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:52.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,it seems as if I'm the one who made it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:53.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:55.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:07:01.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is for last time. Take it, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:08.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, have good dreams for us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:10.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:14.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give him a break, it's a dream after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:16.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:17.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:22.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay, Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:26.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must be receiving the dreams\Nin order to save everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:30.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone seems happy, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:33.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:38.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:43.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,– is what I told my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:50.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I was still afraid of my dreams,\Nand I began taking the medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:54.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:58.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsunami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:10.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:13.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our child, on the shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:15.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never had such a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:21.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:24.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I predict this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:31.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:48.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all because of this medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:52.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I couldn't save Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:58.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I stopped taking the medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:07.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then I began having more prophetic dreams;\Nthey became more and more accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:09.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:12.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,More gifts for us at the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:17.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got to cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:20.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:30.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:31.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're sweating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:33.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bad dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:35.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:38.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just not feeling good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:47.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the following day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:09.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kinu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:15.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the exact sickness that I saw in the dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:19.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Green mold grew from the fingertips...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:23.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,spread around the whole body... and crumbled like dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:25.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was left alone in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:36.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:41.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,When that dream came true, I realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:48.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,that you had deceived me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:58.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Mushi don't give me prophetic dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:11:02.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They bring my dreams into reality and infect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That green sickness...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:09.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It spread to the people around me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:15.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife, my neighbors, across the street...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:22.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the scene in my dreams became\Nthe scene before my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:30.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't "predicting" anything –
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:33.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My dreams were {\i1}making{\i0} them happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:37.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:41.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why did you lie to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:50.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because these Mushi are ineradicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:57.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once you've become infected, all you\Ncan do is live with it in moderation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:04.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if I were to tell you the true nature of the Mushi,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:07.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,you would have collapsed under the\Nsignificance of your creations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:11.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I should have died!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:16.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you let such a disaster live?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:17.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:25.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:31.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll see to it that I rid you of the Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:35.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Live, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yumeno Noawai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:44.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They live within their host's dreams. But every\Nso often, they come out of the dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:51.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when that happens, they become\Nthe carriers of their host's dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:56.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, they don't turn every dream into reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:13:00.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,As they multiply, they leave the dreams more often.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:06.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they become capable of realizing\Ndreams on a higher scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:12.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Mushi are frail; they vanish under sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:17.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not known why they want to come to the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:23.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's said that there is a gathering place for the Mushi,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:28.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that they stay there while their host is awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:34.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I could find that, I could do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:43.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I've never heard of such a fast and enormous case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:46.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The drugs won't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:48.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But overdose would...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:55.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:04.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The medicine. You took all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:06.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:07.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need an antidote!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:08.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:17.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget it. I can't go on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:38.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,His eyes are moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:40.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must be dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:43.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:44.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sleep talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:49.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:53.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nor was it the Mushi's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:56.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were both just trying to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:00.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody is guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:04.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:06.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've done nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:13.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see geese.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:21.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he was talking in his sleep. He's making no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:26.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you right now? Come back quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm in a field of reeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:32.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He responded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:38.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this buzzing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:54.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My conversing with him just bridged his dream to reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:58.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he thinks these are all geese?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:04.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are all swarms of Yumeno Noawai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:33.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:35.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:38.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:40.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kinu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:48.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:51.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:54.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:17:00.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I killed all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:06.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:10.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:18.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:26.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something showing on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:34.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:35.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:37.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:42.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that my dream on the screen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:49.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dream just spread out of my pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:52.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:55.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:01.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:04.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:14.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dream came from the pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...there is a gathering place for the Mushi,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:23.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and that they stay there while their host is awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:35.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never thought they'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:44.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn filfthy Mushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:46.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:17.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:19.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:44.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like your quick aid saved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:46.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:10.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you know this would happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:14.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only cut the pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:19.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:22.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's said that the word "makura"\Ncomes from "tamashii no kura".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:25.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The word "pillow" means a "soul vault".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:30.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You spend almost a third of your life on your pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:33.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was believed that your soul resided in your pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:38.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that is the Yumeno Noawais' nest,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:41.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and it was the pathway between your dreams and reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:46.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew that you'd lose something if you were to cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:56.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Between dreams and reality is the vault of your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:03.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one could see the "Dream World" without this path.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:15.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He later continued working as a blacksmith.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:19.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was well known for his skill...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:23.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But in time his mind became poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:27.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,At times he'd draw his sword on the streets,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:30.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and in the end he faced it towards himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:38.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,People would say...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:42.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,"He feared sleep."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:47.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,"He'd say that his soul would slip down into nothing."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:57.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'd not dreamed once since the day he cut his pillow.
